{"tid":1777574,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中國最新爆紅血腥暴力電玩主題竟是『殺香港人』！","createTime":"2019-12-10T10:07:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T11:47:56.000Z","uid":244058,"like":4,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"72f5a63bb1bc1baefe2036a3045920b286daea1a","tid":1777574,"uid":244058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T10:07:58.000Z","msg":"中國最近廣為流傳一個免費線上遊戲《全民打漢奸》，玩家需要用警棍、斧頭、槍枝、炸藥等血腥暴力武器攻擊殺死香港人，並搜捕擊斃「漢奸」，這些被中國玩家殺死的「漢奸」大部份是以支持香港反送中運動的人作為原型，包括多次主辦合法和平民主集會、先前遭中國政府當局下令砍殺並重傷的香港民陣召集人岑子杰，因莫須有罪名遭中國政府壓進監獄、剝奪其參選權利的香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒，香港壹傳媒創辦人黎智英，香港民主黨創黨主席李柱銘，香港民主黨前主席何俊仁，學生聯盟前秘書長羅冠聰，以及香港政府前政務司司長陳方安生。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dcard.tw/f/trending/p/232649305-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E7%88%86%E7%B4%85%E8%A1%80%E8%85%A5%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E9%9B%BB%E7%8E%A9%E4%B8%BB%E9%A1%8C%E7%AB%9F%E6%98%AF%E3%80%8E%E6%AE%BA%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%8F%EF%BC%81%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E6%9B%B4%E5%8B%95%E5%93%A1%E5%AA%92%E9%AB%94%E7%A4%BE%E7%BE%A4%E5%A4%A7%E8%82%86%E9%BC%93%E5%90%B9%E5%AE%A3%E5%82%B3?utm_source=dcard_fb&amp;utm_medium=post&amp;utm_content=201912101200_trending_232649305\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dcard.tw%2Ff%2Ftrending%2Fp%2F232649305-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%25B4%2585%25E8%25A1%2580%25E8%2585%25A5%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258A%259B%25E9%259B%25BB%25E7%258E%25A9%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E9%25A1%258C%25E7%25AB%259F%25E6%2598%25AF%25E3%2580%258E%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E3%2580%258F%25EF%25BC%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E6%259B%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25AA%2592%25E9%25AB%2594%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2582%2586%25E9%25BC%2593%25E5%2590%25B9%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%2582%25B3%3Futm_source%3Ddcard_fb%26utm_medium%3Dpost%26utm_content%3D201912101200_trending_232649305&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=b4e1756a\" data-auto-link target=\"_