=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456</a><br />\n<br />\nPost：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eDEkrT\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eDEkrT</a><br />\n<br />\n//平等機會婦女聯席發言人區美寶稱，3個組織11月初共同發起控訴警察性暴力的國際聯署，截至本月7日收集到21國共85個團體聯署支持。為了向聯合國專家展開更有力游說，3個組織呼籲受害者主動聯絡他們並接受訪談，強調會保密。//<br />\n<br />\n我們現正收集抗爭者在抗爭期間／被捕後遭受警察性暴力對待的資料，作以下用途：<br />\n1. 協助受害人可以完整保留該事件之紀錄<br />\n2. 整理資料並製成 #ProtestToo 實錄，以作追究之用<br />\n3. 收集國際聯署（進行中），結合個案提交聯合國，爭取國際間關注及支持<br />\n4. 要求香港政府獨立、公正地徹查「反送中運動」發生的性暴力<br />\n<br />\n*個人資料及通訊紀錄在實錄完成後可按受訪者意願全部銷毀<br />\n詳情及相關安排請聯絡Tg @protesttoo"},{"pid":"fd5944c431cf93a68136cac29515672630a85d07","tid":1777574,"uid":129521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T12:56:47.000Z","msg":"班紅衛兵後代係咁上下架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有腦果班死撚哂"},{"pid":"e821fa39ddcfffe165f2e8b4e1ac18acad763c9b","tid":1777574,"uid":39550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81ff63f416c0957c9717c243b75cdaf4c55c7b0a","tid":1777574,"uid":244058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0180d0103fae03e4ceabb608102240e760da3075","tid":1777574,"uid":39550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T10:38:46.000Z","msg":"垃圾民族"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T12:12:26.000Z","msg":"垃圾共產黨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T13:23:22.000Z","msg":"成個國家都係垃撚圾"},{"pid":"cadb2f3f9fb6f2e8e8f7044b3cf18a75417cb923","tid":1777574,"uid":277084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T13:26:52.000Z","msg":"想種族滅絕我哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2abf038ae37874e315b9451799a2ee6bbdb7a21","tid":1777574,"uid":244058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d45135a34c2dcbac5eda0bcc4840f65a64983d54","tid":1777574,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5991f9767831382bfd9a2e9af73248e2caf00239","tid":1777574,"uid":22173,